        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0646P0_20030327_GCR_139' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_77gc' title='Col. 77GC &mdash; HL Deb 27 March 2003 vol 646 c77GC' name='column_77gc' href='#column_77gc' rel='bookmark'>77GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0646P0-03824'>
